OL,3,CAnkle tagging disproportionately
OL,4,Capplied to black offenders released
OL,5,Cfrom prison
OL,7,FITV News has heard claims of racial
OL,8,Fdisparity in how electronic ankle tags
OL,9,Fare deployed, as Kaf Okpattah reports
OL,11,FAs prisons become more crowded there
OL,12,Fis growing pressure to find
OL,13,Falternative forms of punishment and
OL,14,Frehabilitation.
OL,16,FOne such method is the use of
OL,17,Felectronic tags. As of last year there
OL,18,Fwas a 16% increase in offenders
OL,19,Freleased with a tag.
