OL,7,FThere are three types of tags an
OL,8,Foffender can receive:
OL,10,FIf an offender breaches the conditions
OL,11,Fof the tag, they could be taken back
OL,12,Fto court or to prison.
OL,14,FWhile there's no denying the tagging
OL,15,Fscheme has had some success in
OL,16,Fcombating reoffending, some ex-
OL,17,Foffenders ITV News has spoken to who
OL,18,Fare currently on a tag for knife
OL,19,Foffences, told us that it hinders
OL,20,Ftheir rehabilitation.
