OL,7,F"So they put me on tag for carrying a
OL,8,Fknife," said one knife crime offender.
OL,9,F"And the thing that gets you is being
OL,10,Frecalled. And everyday when you're out
OL,11,Fon a GPS tag you're thinking about it.
OL,13,F"One time I was literally five minutes
OL,14,Ffrom charging my tag but because I
OL,15,Fdidn't do it in time, they recalled me
OL,16,Fback to prison."
OL,18,FAnother offender told us that he was
OL,19,Frejected from a job because he was on
OL,20,Ftag.
