OL,3,CAnkle tagging disproportionately
OL,4,Capplied to black offenders released
OL,5,Cfrom prison
OL,7,FThe aim was to reduce reoffending,
OL,8,Fhowever ITV News has learned that it
OL,9,Fis being disproportionately applied to
OL,10,Fblack people; with black knife
OL,11,Foffenders being twice as likely to be
OL,12,Fput on a tag than their white
OL,13,Fcounterparts.
OL,15,FWhile there are more black knife
OL,16,Foffenders in London, the range between
OL,17,Fthem and those who are white is very
OL,18,Fsmall - certainly not large enough,
OL,19,Fexperts say, to justify a racial
OL,20,Fdisparity.
