OL,7,F"I think this is extremely
OL,8,Fconcerning," said Sarah Olney, the MP
OL,9,Ffor Richmond Park who sat on the
OL,10,FElectronic Monitoring select committee.
OL,12,F"We need to be really clear that
OL,13,Fdifferent groups are not being
OL,14,Ftargeted or stigmatised. Any
OL,15,Finequality within the criminal justice
OL,16,Fsystem needs to be looked at, but this
OL,17,Fin particular."
OL,19,FThis injustice within the criminal
OL,20,Fjustice system hasn't gone unnoticed.
