OL,7,FLast year, armed with these figures,
OL,8,Fthe Black Equity Organisation filed a
OL,9,Fsuccessful lawsuit against the
OL,10,FMinistry of Justice and the Mayor's
OL,11,FOffice for Policing and Crime.
OL,13,FBoth departments have now committed to
OL,14,Fa rapid review of the knife crime
OL,15,Ftagging scheme, as well as removing
OL,16,Fgang membership as one of the
OL,17,Fselection factors in the scheme.
