OL,7,FIn a statement a spokesperson for the
OL,8,FMayor of London said: "The Mayor is
OL,9,Fsupporting work to identify and reduce
OL,10,Fdisproportionality across the whole of
OL,11,Fthe Criminal Justice System.
OL,13,F"MOPAC is continuing to evaluate and
OL,14,Fpublish analysis from the programme
OL,15,Fand working closely with partners
OL,16,Fincluding the Ministry of Justice to
OL,17,Fensure GPS tagging is fair and
OL,18,Fproportionate as we build a safer
OL,19,FLondon for all."
